295
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:54,750
Why didn't you listen?

296
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:56,600
I didn't know.

297
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:57,440
No,

298
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:58,460
it was...

299
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,320
Minglei asked me to sell it.

300
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,050
Nonsense!

301
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:05,470
When did I ask you to sell it?

302
00:17:06,930 --> 00:17:08,170
Did I tell you to?

303
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:12,490
Enough.

304
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,500
Stop acting like you're wronged.

305
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:18,020
You said it had nothing to do with you,

306
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:20,240
and he said it had nothing to do with him.

307
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,640
Aren't you making things difficult for me?

308
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,750
Here's what we'll do.

309
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,210
I'll leave your man to you.

310
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,880
If you want to argue,
argue amongst yourselves.

311
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,890
Just give me an explanation in the end.

312
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:31,150
I only have one demand.

313
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,920
From now on,

314
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,640
my rules are the rules.

315
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:38,270
No one can mess up my business,

316
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,240
and no one

317
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,400
can turn a deaf ear to my words.

318
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,310
Does Boss He know

319
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,770
you're doing this??

320
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,550
Dahua.

321
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:54,190
You stay here and watch them.

322
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,140
Don't let them kill each other.

323
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:56,610
Okay.

324
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:57,830
Cheng,

325
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,810
why are you leaving?

326
00:17:58,810 --> 00:17:59,960
Cheng, don't go.

327
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:01,680
Save me, Cheng!

328
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:02,430
Cheng.

329
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:05,000
How did you know he was selling powder?

330
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:05,720
Help!

331
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:27,690
That's him.

332
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,680
Print out his frontal face.

333
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,210
Print out a few more angles.

334
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,270
Senior.

335
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,590
You asked me to investigate that car.

336
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:46,240
I found the owner

337
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,200
and got the dashcam.

338
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,480
It actually captured the guy's
frontal face.

339
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:49,200
Have you confirmed his identity?

340
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:49,830
Yes.

341
00:18:49,830 --> 00:18:50,480
It's the killer

342
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:51,960
in a serial murder case in Huaiguang City
20 years ago

343
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:52,690
named Qi Yan.

344
00:18:53,070 --> 00:18:53,550
Who?

345
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,070
Qi Yan.

346
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:00,400
Qi Yan!

347
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,810
This is impossible.

348
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:18,960
This is the killer of the
Huaiguang serial murder case.

349
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,920
This case was originally an unsolved case.

350
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,830
I handled it myself 20 years ago.

351
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:23,480
The 8.17 Case

352
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,010
