353
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,040
It was closed.

354
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:28,000
Yao Weihai took his men to the scene

355
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,260
and caught the killer.

356
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,750
You mean him?

357
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,350
His name is Qi Yan.

358
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:34,090
He resisted arrest at the scene.

359
00:19:34,090 --> 00:19:36,300
The police shot him to death on the spot.

360
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:37,880
He's dead?

361
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:39,140
Dead!

362
00:19:39,170 --> 00:19:40,760
Dead as a doornail!

363
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:42,440
Where is Yao Weihai?

364
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:44,270
He went to the Provincial Bureau.

365
00:19:44,270 --> 00:19:45,530
Could you be mistaken?

366
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:46,720
No!

367
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,200
Even if he turned to ashes,

368
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:50,260
I could still smell the stench on him.

369
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:52,220
Throughout the whole crime,

370
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:54,920
