371
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:55,830
How could he appear

372
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:57,310
in the dashcam?

373
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:59,250
Was it really by accident?

374
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:00,450
Or

375
00:20:00,610 --> 00:20:02,740
did he deliberately let us see his face

376
00:20:02,860 --> 00:20:04,600
and remind us of Qi Yan?

377
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,780
Has the video been tampered with?

378
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:08,880
No.

379
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,470
There's no issue with it.

380
00:20:10,470 --> 00:20:12,130
The forensic results are out.

381
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,680
The semen stain we extracted
from the deceased

382
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,270
was compared with the DNA database.

383
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,130
It is confirmed

384
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:22,640
to be Qi Yan's.

385
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:36,810
I want to talk to my student

386
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:38,510
