387
00:20:38,730 --> 00:20:39,380
Okay.

388
00:20:39,410 --> 00:20:41,210
Come, let's analyze it outside.

389
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,270
Don't worry.

390
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:43,030
Come.

391
00:20:43,030 --> 00:20:43,630
Come here.

392
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:58,960
It's okay.

393
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,200
I'll go out first.

394
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,510
Dead?

395
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,400
And they saw it with their own eyes?

396
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,400
How do we investigate that?

397
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,030
How can we catch a dead man?

398
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,260
About this video,

399
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:27,480
whether it's intentional or unintentional,

400
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,340
we can't let it lead us by the nose.

401
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,030
We will investigate

402
00:21:31,030 --> 00:21:31,920
as we should.

403
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,830
You're right.

404
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:52,030
Do you remember what I told you before?

405
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:56,310
If one path is a dead end,

406
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,060
what should you do?

407
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:00,550
Try another path.

408
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,530
Things that seem

409
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,480
impossible now

410
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,790
will all make sense

411
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:12,520
when the real killer is caught.

412
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:16,050
Didn't I tell you before?

413
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,330
This Qi Yan

414
00:22:18,070 --> 00:22:19,310
was targeting you.

415
00:22:19,870 --> 00:22:22,230
Why did he show his face on the monitor?

416
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,840
And showing only half of it?

417
00:22:24,630 --> 00:22:26,760
He's throwing down a challenge to you.

418
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,040
But at least I can confirm

419
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:33,580
that this person is definitely
connected to Qi Yan.

420
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:35,960
I...

421
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,750
I want to go back to Huaiguang

422
00:22:39,590 --> 00:22:41,030
to investigate

423
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:42,920
Qi Yan's case again.

424
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:44,830
See if I can

425
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:47,350
find any new clues.

426
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:50,830
Okay.

427
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:56,790
Just like that,

428
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:59,240
