429
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,720
This Qi Yan...

430
00:23:02,750 --> 00:23:03,850
He erased his entire life history.

431
00:23:03,850 --> 00:23:05,850
He's completely clean now

432
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:09,270
as if he just appeared out of thin air.

433
00:23:10,270 --> 00:23:11,480
The matter Yao Weihai

434
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:13,160
didn't figure out back then

435
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,820
is still very difficult for us

436
00:23:16,310 --> 00:23:17,720
to investigate now.

437
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,350
But

438
00:23:21,030 --> 00:23:23,560
we must investigate,
no matter how hard it is.

439
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,880
Book me a train ticket

440
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:37,960
for today

441
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:38,790
to Huaiguang.

442
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:40,550
Right.

443
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:42,350
Right.

444
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:44,590
Send me the details after you buy it.

445
00:23:45,510 --> 00:23:47,480
Grandpa, are you back?

446
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,600
My little sweetheart.

447
00:23:52,410 --> 00:23:53,440
I'm not back there.

448
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,720
I'm working.

449
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,000
Grandpa,

450
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,790
