451
00:23:59,190 --> 00:24:00,030
Of course.

452
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,720
You can buy as many as you want.

453
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,200
Mom won't let me.

454
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,750
She said ducklings poop everywhere.

455
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,480
All ducklings poop.

456
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:09,200
The ones that don't poop are toys.

457
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:10,750
I will buy them for you when I get back.

458
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,750
I'll buy a whole basket of them for you.

459
00:24:11,750 --> 00:24:13,880
Grandpa, sing me a song.

460
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,590
No singing.

461
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:15,510
Please sing!

462
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,110
Okay, okay.

463
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,150
I'll sing.

464
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:22,590
♪ Under the bridge at the door ♪

465
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:25,110
♪ A bunch of ducks came ♪

466
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:27,350
♪ Come and count them ♪

467
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,200
♪ Two, four, six, seven, eight ♪

468
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,830
♪ Come and count them ♪

469
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,640
♪ Two, four, six, seven, eight ♪

470
00:24:45,510 --> 00:24:46,160
No more singing.

471
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,420
I still have work to do.

472
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:49,070
Goodbye, Grandpa.

473
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:49,830
Goodbye.

474
00:24:49,930 --> 00:24:51,590
Dad, you can't spoil her like this.

475
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,400
Stop nagging!

476
00:24:54,270 --> 00:24:56,270
Hurry up and buy me the train ticket!

477
00:25:00,110 --> 00:25:00,750
Prof.

478
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:02,550
No rush.

479
00:25:02,890 --> 00:25:03,890
Go back tomorrow.

480
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,550
Whenever I think of this Qi Yan,

481
00:25:07,550 --> 00:25:08,750
I feel so suffocated.

482
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:10,470
The sooner it's resolved,

483
00:25:10,470 --> 00:25:12,070
the sooner I'll feel at ease.

484
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,190
This piece of garbage

485
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:21,650
ruined my best student.

486
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,530
Prof,

487
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,920
did I disappoint you again?

488
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,070
No.

489
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,940
You've never disappointed me.

490
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:38,850
Really.

491
00:25:39,980 --> 00:25:42,220
You've never disappointed me.

492
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:48,110
Never.

493
00:26:01,790 --> 00:26:02,440
Hansheng,

494
00:26:07,050 --> 00:26:08,780
you've never disappointed me.

495
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:10,590
You used to be

496
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:14,230
a cold machine.

497
00:26:15,510 --> 00:26:16,550
But now,

498
00:26:17,530 --> 00:26:20,090
you're a living human being,

499
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,160
you know?

500
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:24,440
Now you have

501
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:25,790
emotions and desires.

502
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:39,030
Tell me,

503
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,230
are you and Zhou

504
00:26:41,250 --> 00:26:42,940
going to have a belated wedding ceremony?

505
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:44,900
I'm busy with work this year.

506
00:26:45,330 --> 00:26:46,440
Hurry up.

507
00:26:46,470 --> 00:26:48,510
I'm waiting to hold your baby.

508
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:51,310
I'm telling you...

509
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:51,970
It will be soon.

510
00:26:51,970 --> 00:26:53,830
I even thought of their nickname.

511
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:56,200
If it's a boy,

512
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,920
we'll call him Little Pickle.

513
00:26:57,920 --> 00:26:58,840
Little Pickle?

514
00:26:58,870 --> 00:26:59,430
Yes.

515
00:26:59,450 --> 00:27:00,680
If it's a girl,

516
00:27:00,700 --> 00:27:02,390
we'll call her Rice Porridge.

517
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:03,970
Isn't it nice?

518
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:07,320
I have to ask Zhou Jin about this.

519
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:09,650
Director Wang,

520
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:11,000
when you arrive in Huaiguang,

521
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:13,920
just contact Zhou if you need anything.

522
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:14,850
Okay.

523
00:27:16,230 --> 00:27:17,890
I'll go straight to the hotel.

524
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:18,980
I'll grab my things

525
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,680
and head to the train station.

526
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,550
No need to see me out.

527
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:23,150
Thank you for your hard work.

528
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:24,760
Mr. Wang,

529
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:25,720
