530
00:27:26,450 --> 00:27:27,840
Let me do it, Prof.

531
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:30,080
Are you worried, unhappy, .

532
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,430
or just unwilling

533
00:27:32,430 --> 00:27:34,090
