534
00:27:34,140 --> 00:27:34,820
Exactly.

535
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,090
Give me the keys.

536
00:27:40,500 --> 00:27:41,530
Wait for me a moment, Mr. Wang.

537
00:27:41,530 --> 00:27:42,620
I'm going to change clothes.

538
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:43,590
Okay, hurry up.

539
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:56,050
Zhou.

540
00:27:56,890 --> 00:27:59,030
You've been working for a few years,
right?

541
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,990
I graduated from Jingzhou Police Academy.

542
00:28:00,990 --> 00:28:01,940
After graduation,

543
00:28:01,940 --> 00:28:04,200
I worked at a grassroots police station.

544
00:28:04,330 --> 00:28:06,820
Then I was transferred to
the Public Security Brigade.

545
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:07,740
A year ago,

546
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:10,480
I just came to
the Criminal Investigation Brigade.

547
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,410
That's not easy.

548
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:15,920
Mr. Wang.

549
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:18,680
About the Huaiguang
serial murder case,

550
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,900
is it true that apart from the task force,

551
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,250
even police officers

552
00:28:22,590 --> 00:28:23,590
are not authorized to know

553
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:25,190
more details about the case?

554
00:28:25,210 --> 00:28:27,210
This case was closed a long time ago.

555
00:28:28,130 --> 00:28:29,210
In principle,

556
00:28:30,130 --> 00:28:33,510
it's past the criminal investigation
confidentiality phase.

557
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:35,510
It's not that we can't talk about it.

558
00:28:35,570 --> 00:28:37,640
But this case involves the 8.17 Case

559
00:28:38,450 --> 00:28:40,860
and the safety of the informant.

560
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:43,140
That's why it wasn't made public.

561
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,000
Was the informant

562
00:28:46,670 --> 00:28:47,600
Hansheng?

563
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:52,420
He told you?

564
00:28:54,830 --> 00:28:57,660
Knowing is better than not.

565
00:28:59,230 --> 00:29:00,950
He just told me briefly.

566
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,350
After all, there are many things

567
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:05,010
