568
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:06,700
Mr. Wang.

569
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:09,880
I want to know

570
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:12,260
more details about these two cases.

571
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:15,890
Because my brother Zhou Chuan

572
00:29:16,390 --> 00:29:19,920
was the special police officer
who sacrificed in the 8.17 Case.

573
00:29:21,430 --> 00:29:22,760
What do you want to know?

574
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,310
I want to know...

575
00:29:26,890 --> 00:29:28,950
Besides what you said at the meeting,

576
00:29:29,030 --> 00:29:30,830
is there anything else special?

577
00:29:31,090 --> 00:29:32,160
For example,

578
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:34,040
did Qi Yan

579
00:29:34,810 --> 00:29:36,140
show any special hatred

580
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:37,750
towards the police

581
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:39,440
in the Huaiguang Case?

582
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:43,430
Hatred towards the police?

583
00:29:47,190 --> 00:29:47,990
My brother...

584
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,970
His death was horrific.

585
